              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29398439/" class="">第236页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/14368383/" class=" " title="蟹壳黄">蟹壳黄</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="29398439">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">虽然原因让人同情，但放弃理性总是软弱的行径。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29398439/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-11-18 12:58</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>虽然原因让人同情，但放弃理性总是软弱的行径。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







