          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/32205749/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/32205749/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/79493855/" class=" " title="fairy">fairy</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="32205749">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">在公共场合什么都不说，到了私下里则妙语连珠，换言之，对信得过的人什么都说，对信不过的人什么都不说。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-07-12 22:36</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>在公共场合什么都不说，到了私下里则妙语连珠，换言之，对信得过的人什么都说，对信不过的人什么都不说。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







